CHAI
Mocha is a test framework while Chai is an expectation API provides libraries for assertion  etc.
Chai supports various assertion styles (expect, assert, should)

sudo npm install -g chai

http://chaijs.com/guide/styles/

Sinon can be used for faking the environment!

